hey,

Well, I'll be the little ray of sunshine on this day...

Apparently lots of people hate Valentine's day, and that's cool, but I like it, I think it's nice. Yeah, so, I don't have anyone but I still have freinds and family and isn't there love there too? I dunno, but I think that's a reason to be happy... but oh well, I'm not gonna let one simple day get me down. Mandy

Last night sucked. Oh well, we can't have it all now can we?

Today was good, even tho I was super tired! And YAY FOR MID-TERM BREAK IN T-MINUS 4 DAYS AND COUNTING!!!! :P


Later Dayz,
Mandy

My classes are goin alright so far but I should study a lot more then what I am, seems I just can't get my mind on it... I need to focus but my head is in the clouds...

My week started out crappy but it's gettin better, Wednesday I had my first 2 classes then English and Bio were cancelled and yesterday Math and Psyc were cancelled!! Wahoo! But school opened just in time for my Bio Lab, which is great because if we never had it yesterday we would have to make it up on Saturday (gross) so Thankfully we had it on time :)

This weekend someone better get ready for the chaos I'm gonna cause... yeah, I'm gonna be STUDYING all weekend, at home so, you better watch out. *cough* Actually this weekend will be nice and relaxing, something I need...

Mandy

Hey,

I woke up this morning at 7:30am... decided I didn't want to get up at 10 like I had my clock set to alarm... and wen back to bed.

2:00 I get up, get ready and go outside and shovel my 6 car driveway... I learned during this that slush is heavy... and that I really like shoveling... I know I'm weird.

Then I come inside where there's a message left on my MSN from Claralee (my cousin) to call her. She had a virus, and I went over to see what I could do to help... I couldn't do anything, I got part of it deleted but it's a virus that affects more that one file and I couldn't find the other files... so she is going to get a friend of her's to look at it... anywayz nuff rambling bout that.

I ate supper at Claralee's, puttered around the house for a while... and now I'm waiting for my Grandmother to call me...


anywayz,

Later Dayz,
Mandy

hey,

Okay... where do I begin? I think I'll start Dec.30.

Dec. 30, I get up 8:00am and get ready to go to Markland and that area. I get to the Irving at about 1:30 where Joey comes and picks me up and gives me a tour of the area. Then we go back to his place and hang out and get ready for the Band Show. Then we go to Mitchel's then we went and picked Topher up and I meet Don (Pokit Rockit's gutairest sp??) And we head to Shearstown (I think) to the Band Show where we meet up with Kris and Mitchel. Then we enjoy the show (pics in "My Space") Even tho I got a headache. Anywayz, after the show we all went to McDonald's and then the guys drop me and Kris off at her house.

Next Day Me and Kris spend hours playing with my camera. Then we watch Chicago then played Phase Ten with her family (I sucked at it) And then we ate supper and got ready for New Years. Then Mitchel calls and tells us New Years location was changed from Topher's to the Loft so me and Kris had to get ready all over again. haha.

That night we go to the loft (no comment on the loft) Then we go to Joey's for a bit, then we went to the lake and set off fireworks, (scary and bad idea) We almost get hit by one and then another set anded in the trees. But I suppose that's what you get for getting a bunch of drunk guys settin them off... haha. Then we went to Topher's to dance and hang out.

Next moring I hang with Kris, watch some Friends and then get ready and I go to Joey's forsupper and sleep over the night. We have supper at Joey's aunt's where they keep giving me Orange Creamcicles and I get a little buzzed and pick on Joey for the night while his mom takes a 100 pics of me but I like getting pic takin so it's all good. Then after we go back to Joey's and watch Batman and Aladdin and some comics.

Today I get up get ready and go home with Joey and his parents then I went to Joey's for supper and hang out and now here I am!!

That's it... i think...

Later Dayz,
Mandy

PS. Kris if you're readin this I'll call you tomorrow!

hey,

Well, first Christmas not in Labrador... we good! Very good in fact. Bit weird tho...

Christmas eve, we did the regular cooking,wrapping (I did the MOST wrapping over the xmas season) and then we all got ready and went to Obie's christining. It was nice and I had to read which I was kinda nervous for but it turned out good.

THEN, came the party at my place, LOTS of people and good times, drinkin, food, laughs, singing, family and more. I had an awesome time. Then we went down to Newtown til like 3:30am.

Christmas morning I woke up at 6 and waited for my cousin Ness to call, which happened at 7:00. I woke up and while looking out my window for my family to come to my house to open gifts (we had a gross amount of gifts) My mom metioned Ashley and I bawled... it was very unexpected on my be half.

But for Christmas I got a digital camera, clothes, bullitin board, photo frame, 2 games and more... anywayz, I gtg.


Later Dayz, (and Merry Christmas)
Mandy

hey,

Got my marks back. 74 in Frech, 69 in Ling(grrr...), 81 in Math and 71 in Psyc. :) I haven't got English back the one I'm most worried about... of course... anywayz...

Joey, I "misplaced" you home phone so I'll call the cell... oops!


Later Dayz,
Mandy

hey,

I'm here in Templeman... blah! Haha, nah it isn't that bad. It's my nan's b-day day today so we came home gave her her gifts and now were just sitting around. The ride out here was uncomfortable, our car was so packed I couldn't even get my feet on the floor, it was crazy.

Well, approx. 3 weeks til I see Joey again... that is if I can't go to kris's for New years (she called this morning btw) Hopefully though I get out there for New years!!! It'll be great,

Well, that's about it, I won't be on MSN very often cuz there's only dial up here and it's not my computer and I'll be busy... oh well... Hope you all have an awesome Christmas!

And Joey I miss you too... xoxo

Later Dayz, 
Mandy

hey,

Today I had my lingustics exam... lets just say it was unbelieveably BRUTAL!!! AHHHHH... Half of it was working with a language from the Sounthern Congo... ugh! Oh well it's done I'm done... yay!

Tomorrow is the semi formal... I can't wait, I already trie dress on my dress, and yes it still looks good :P

I brought Honey over to Joey's it was a good meeting. While I was there we watched the Punisher, took Honey for a walk where I met a few of Joey's friends and his cousin, we also watched Dane Cook. And I guess this is as good as any place to announce (for a lack of better word) That me and Joey now go out. It's official. haha :P

Later Dayz,
Mandy

hey,

So, I wake up today at 9:30... oh my... then my Aunt Shelia, Uncle Kev, Claralee, Obie, Ashley and Mom all go to Stavanger and shop have luch(which felt like supper) So, here I am in Wal-Mart convinced it's like 8:30 at night, but in reality it's only 1:00!!! Then we go home and Uncle Kev wants me to take him to the mall cuz he doesn't like driving out here, so we go to the mall and shop and browse around.

I get home, at 5:30 or so, make a CD for Aunt Shelia after many attempts and go pick up some pizza from Pizza Delight. And then I babysit Obie for 2 hours which he cried through, I hate when babies cry cuz you don't know why they're upset. Then I wrap some presents for people, and after I do odds and ends I end up here now writing this.

But on a brighter note I have 3 new pairs of pants!! :P

Tomorrow is a study day for lingustics... I can't wait til I'm done that boring crap!! And also it is my LAST exam so, that's always a bright note... Everyone else has been done for a while and are gone home.

Friday, is exam, and hanging with Joey and HOPEFULLY *crosses fingers* I can bring Honey over, and the Saturday is the semi-formal!!!! YAY!

Also, today I found out 100% I can go to Topher's for New Years!!! YAY! (now... all I need is a ride...)

Later Dayz,
Mandy

hey,

I had my French exam and it went well! Yay! Thanks Ryan for keeping me sane! (Remember une robe, not une jupe!! haha)

Well, my last exam is Friday and I have the courde passed already! YAY! I'm so happy.

Last night while studying I drank 2 pepsi's, a juice box and ate a piece of cake, and I was the most hyper... it was bad I was shaking.

And Today I got to see Sandra at Bree's. Joey, Bree, Tim, Brendon were also there, then after Bree's I went to Joey's for little while then I came home and had McDonald's. And now here I am...


Later Dayz,
Mandy
